<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cosy Languages - Presente Indicativo: Verbo 'Essere'</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Playfair:ital,opsz,wght@1,16..24,300&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg-teal: #129a9a; 
            --parchment-base: #fbf8f0;
            --parchment-dark: #f3edd9;
            --ink-dark: #2a2521;
            --ink-muted: #5c534c;
            --accent-warm: #8b5a2b;
            
            /* Guida semantica dei colori */
            --color-verb: #1a5fb4;       /* Blu inchiostro per il verbo 'Essere' */
            --color-negation: #c0392b;   /* Rosso terracotta per la negazione */
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Didot, Georgia, serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255,248,220,0.15) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 60%), var(--bg-teal);
            color: var(--ink-dark);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Effetto fogli di pergamena sovrapposti */
        .infographic-container {
            background-color: var(--parchment-base);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--parchment-base), var(--parchment-dark));
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 850px;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 
                2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.05),
                5px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),
                12px 12px 0px -4px #f5f0df,
                12px 12px 20px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.15),
                20px 20px 0px -8px #eee7cd,
                20px 20px 30px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        /* Intestazione / Brand */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .logo-mark {
            font-size: 3.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: -5px;
            color: var(--ink-dark);
            text-transform: lowercase;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--ink-muted);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: var(--ink-dark);
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h1::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 25%;
            width: 50%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--accent-warm), transparent);
        }

        /* Griglia strutturale principale */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 35px;
        }

        .full-width {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        /* Schede di contenuto */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.15);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Formules grammaticali */
        .formula-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.04);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--ink-muted);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.2);
        }

        .formula-bar span.op {
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Classi di accentuazione dei colori */
        .v-sono, .v-sei, .v-e, .v-siamo, .v-siete, .v-gen {
            color: var(--color-verb);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .neg {
            color: var(--color-negation);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Griglia per la Forma Affermativa */
        .system-box {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .system-column {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        .system-column h3 {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--ink-muted);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .math-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 2.2;
        }

        .math-left {
            flex: 1.2;
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 15px;
        }

        .math-sign {
            color: var(--accent-warm);
            font-weight: 300;
            font-family: monospace;
        }

        .math-right {
            flex: 1;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        /* Allineamento delle liste */
        .align-list {
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 2.2;
        }

        .align-list li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .align-item {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 140px;
        }

        .align-item.right-aligned {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .align-center {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            width: 30px;
        }

        /* Architettura delle tabelle */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 14px 18px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--ink-muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.15);
        }

        td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        /* Banner di avviso */
        .warning-banner {
            background: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.15);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 35px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .warning-icon {
            color: var(--color-negation);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .right-text {
            background: rgba(26, 95, 180, 0.08);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Design Responsivo */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .system-box {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .infographic-container {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            .math-row {
                font-size: 1.05rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="infographic-container">
        
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-mark">a</div>
            <div class="logo-text">Cosy Languages</div>
            <h1>Il Verbo 'Essere': <span class="v-sono">sono</span> / <span class="v-e">è</span> / <span class="v-sono">sono</span></h1>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-container">
            
            <div class="card full-width">
                <div class="card-title">1. Forma Affermativa (Il Sistema)</div>
                <div class="system-box">
                    <div class="system-column">
                        <h3>Soggetti Singolari</h3>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Io</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-sono">sono</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Tu</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-sei">sei</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Lui / Lei</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-e">è</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="system-column">
                        <h3>Soggetti Plurali</h3>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Noi</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-siamo">siamo</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Voi</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-siete">siete</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="math-row">
                            <div class="math-left">Loro</div>
                            <div class="math-sign">&rarr;</div>
                            <div class="math-right v-sono">sono</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">2. Forma Negativa</div>
                <div class="formula-bar">
                    <span>Soggetto</span> <span class="op">+</span> <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="op">+</span> <span class="v-gen">Verbo</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="align-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Io</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sono">sono</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Tu</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sei">sei</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Lui / Lei</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-e">è</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Noi</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-siamo">siamo</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Voi</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-siete">siete</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">Loro</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item"><span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sono">sono</span></span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">3. Forma Interrogativa</div>
                <div class="formula-bar">
                    <span>(Soggetto)</span> <span class="op">+</span> <span class="v-gen">Verbo</span> <span class="op">+</span> <span>?</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="align-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Io)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-sono">sono?</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Tu)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-sei">sei?</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Lui / Lei)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-e">è?</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Noi)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-siamo">siamo?</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Voi)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-siete">siete?</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="align-item right-aligned">(Loro)</span>
                        <span class="align-center">&nbsp;</span>
                        <span class="align-item v-sono">sono?</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card full-width">
                <div class="card-title">4. Matrice Strutturale Globale</div>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Pronome Soggetto</th>
                            <th>Affermativo (+)</th>
                            <th>Negativo (-)</th>
                            <th>Interrogativo (?)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Io</strong></td>
                            <td>io <span class="v-sono">sono</span></td>
                            <td>io <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sono">sono</span></td>
                            <td>io <span class="v-sono">sono</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Tu</strong></td>
                            <td>tu <span class="v-sei">sei</span></td>
                            <td>tu <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sei">sei</span></td>
                            <td>tu <span class="v-sei">sei</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Lui / Lei</strong></td>
                            <td>lui <span class="v-e">è</span></td>
                            <td>lui <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-e">è</span></td>
                            <td>lui <span class="v-e">è</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Noi</strong></td>
                            <td>noi <span class="v-siamo">siamo</span></td>
                            <td>noi <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-siamo">siamo</span></td>
                            <td>noi <span class="v-siamo">siamo</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Voi</strong></td>
                            <td>voi <span class="v-siete">siete</span></td>
                            <td>voi <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-siete">siete</span></td>
                            <td>voi <span class="v-siete">siete</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Loro</strong></td>
                            <td>loro <span class="v-sono">sono</span></td>
                            <td>loro <span class="neg">non</span> <span class="v-sono">sono</span></td>
                            <td>loro <span class="v-sono">sono</span>?</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="warning-banner">
            <span class="warning-icon">&#9888;</span>
            <div>
                <strong>Nota linguistica:</strong> In italiano i pronomi soggetto (io, tu, lui...) sono solitamente <strong>omessi</strong>, tranne quando si vuole enfatizzare il soggetto. La negazione <span class="right-text"><span class="neg">non</span></span> si colloca sempre <strong>prima</strong> del verbo.
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
